Tyrael nodded.

Tyrael: Gladly. I was planning to send a transmission to Deathsteel
telling him to incapacitate the shields and defenses... permanently if
possible. Then, we strike. Darkangel and Dreadplague take the fight to
the air while you, me, Dragoon and Synergy concentrate on killing them
one at a time. Understand that I want Hydras dead more than any other
predacon. He is the primary target. Killing him will leave the
Predacons confused and weakened.

awaiting
